question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Kje se nahaja mestna hiša Gyeongju v mestu Gyeongju v Južni Koreji?
answer: Mestna hiša Gyeongju se nahaja na naslovu 8-13 Wanggyeong-ro, Hwangnam-dong, Gyeongju, Gyeongsangbuk-do, Južna Koreja.
answer_translated_eng: Mestna hiša Gyeongju se nahaja na naslovu 8-13 Wanggyeong-ro, Hwangnam-dong, Gyeongju, Gyeongsangbuk-do, Yuzhna Koreja.
